{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/Float/Model/Unpacked/Round.html#Float.Model.UnpackedFloat.normalize\"><span class=\"name\">Float</span>.<span class=\"name\">Model</span>.<span class=\"name\">UnpackedFloat</span>.<span class=\"name\">normalize</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">spec</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Data/Float/Model/Format/Basic.html#Float.Model.Format\">Format</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">mantissa </span><span class=\"fn\">exponent</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Data/Int/Basic.html#Int\">Int</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">zeroSign</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Data/Float/Model/Unpacked/Sign.html#Float.Model.UnpackedFloat.Sign\">Sign</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Data/Float/Model/Unpacked/Basic.html#Float.Model.UnpackedFloat\">UnpackedFloat</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Given a finite float represented as a signed mantissa and an exponent, round it to conform to the\ngiven `Format`.\n\nIf necessary, this will both decrease and increase the exponent.\n","docLink":"./Init/Data/Float/Model/Unpacked/Round.html#Float.Model.UnpackedFloat.normalize","kind":"def","line":183,"name":"Float.Model.UnpackedFloat.normalize","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Init/Data/Float/Model/Unpacked/Round.lean#L183-L193"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/Float/Model/Unpacked/Round.html#Float.Model.UnpackedFloat.round\"><span class=\"name\">Float</span>.<span class=\"name\">Model</span>.<span class=\"name\">UnpackedFloat</span>.<span class=\"name\">round</spa